Description: Incident-first root-cause analysis console for Linux
 v0.42.2 fixes a browser-caching bug: the hub previously served /static/*
 with "Cache-Control: max-age=31536000, immutable", pinning stale JS for
 a year. Now uses no-cache/must-revalidate + per-build cache-bust query
 strings so every hub upgrade instantly pushes new assets.
